  "identifier": "HB 12",
  "title": "AN ACT relating to privacy for members of the General Assembly.",
  "abstract": "Amend KRS 61.7991 to add current members of the General Assembly and their immediate family members to the definition of \"covered person\"; authorize standing for a civil action for injunctive or declaratory relief for unauthorized disclosure; provide that the removal of information does not apply to required disclosures under KRS Chapter 6 or 61.",
